{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"Registers the device for push notifications with initial tags.","type":"text"}],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"registerForPushNotificationsWith:"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"registerForPushNotificationsWith:","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)registerForPushNotificationsWith:","title":"registerForPushNotificationsWith:"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"registerForPushNotificationsWith:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"NSDictionary","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSDictionary"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"tags"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}]},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Dictionary of tag names and values to set during registration."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Supported value types: NSString, NSNumber, NSArray (for list tags).","type":"text"}]}],"name":"tags"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Combines push notification registration with tag assignment in a single operation."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This is more efficient than calling registerForPushNotifications and setTags separately,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"as tags are sent to the server along with the registration request.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Use this method when you have user attributes available at the time of registration,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"such as during onboarding or after user authentication."}]},{"level":2,"text":"Example","anchor":"Example","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Register with user attributes after sign-up:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["class SignUpCoordinator {","","    func completeSignUp(user: User, source: SignUpSource) {","        let registrationTags: [String: Any] = [","            \"user_type\": user.accountType.rawValue,","            \"signup_source\": source.analyticsValue,","            \"signup_date\": ISO8601DateFormatter().string(from: Date()),","            \"interests\": user.selectedInterests,","            \"language\": Locale.current.languageCode ?? \"en\",","            \"app_version\": Bundle.main.appVersion","        ]","","        Pushwoosh.configure.registerForPushNotifications(with: registrationTags)","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setUserId(user.id)","        Pushwoosh.configure.setEmail(user.email)","    }","}","","extension Bundle {","    var appVersion: String {","        infoDictionary?[\"CFBundleShortVersionString\"] as? String ?? \"unknown\"","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"}]}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/registerForPushNotificationsWith:"},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/registerforpushnotificationswith:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"role":"symbol","abstract":[],"title":"PWConfiguration","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier"